channel.title: Failure to Preserve Mission Critical Personel
channel.description: At the lambda complex entrance, if I kill the scientist after he lets me in I'm still punished for failing to preserve mission critical personnel. He is no longer mission critical after I am in the lambda complex. He got the short straw. Deal with it.
